  <channel>
    <title>Headhunters </title>
    <link>https://www.pbsfm.org.au/program/headhunters</link>
    <description>&lt;p style="text-align:start"&gt;Global sounds and more.&lt;br&gt;
The search is for music that might not like to belong to a particular category … and artists who prefer to deviate from the path.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style="text-align:start"&gt;Here, we're "&lt;em&gt;not afraid of 'mutant' styles and cultivate an eye (or an ear?) for the unusual, the less known, 'the little side roads' that music takes, the cult sound, for the thing that contradicts the stereotype, the unexpected and the raw and the rough.&lt;/em&gt;" &lt;small&gt;David Byrne (Luaka Bop)&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
